txt.en: You have been tasked with defeating the Angmarim Warg-breeders in Gundabad.
The mission is complete!\n\nSpeak to Ausma for your reward!

'I have a new mission for you, [placeholder].\n\n'My scouts have returned from Cútaig. It seems the most vicious Wargs in Gundabad are being bred in those passages. The time has come to seek out the Angmarim Warg-breeders there and drive them off.'

Within the halls of Cútaig, the most vicious Wargs of Gundabad are bred. There, even the most skilled of hunters must tread with care lest they become the hunted….\n\nYour mission is to defeat the Angmarim Warg-breeders in Gundabad.
The monster commander in this mission has poison attacks that will do additional damage if not cured with a salve, potion, or skill.
Your mission is to defeat the Angmarim Warg-breeders in Gundabad.\n\nSpeak to Ausma to travel.
'You have done well, [placeholder]. The fewer Wargs in Gundabad, the better!\n\n'With the Warg-breeders defeated, the Angmarim will know that we are not to be underestimated!'
